Package: tcp-syn-stop
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, nftables, curl
Description: High-performance eBPF TCP SYN flood protection daemon
 tcp_syn_stop leverages eBPF (XDP and Kprobes) to detect and drop
 malicious SYN flood traffic at the network driver level, before it
 impacts the system's CPU and networking stack.
